  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076890/extras/0d227091270d03c332962604e8b4e891.poster.avif?t=1668033083\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076890/extras/0d227091270d03c332962604e8b4e891.webm?t=1668033083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2076890/extras/0d227091270d03c332962604e8b4e891.mp4?t=1668033083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rapid Retort is a time trial FPS with an emphasis on speed and self improvement. Face a gauntlet of challenges designed to challenge your fundamental FPS skills. No filler, just you and your ability to hit targets and avoid obstacles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 50 levels in environments ranging from tight corridors to open farmland<br></li><li>30 different firearms including high penetration magnums and lever actions<br></li><li>Varying traps and tricks to test your awareness</li></ul>",
